{"tid":2357914,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"賀年糕點黃店整合","createTime":"2021-01-07T18:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T16:48:41.000Z","uid":200189,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"df1f65051ea486ac83d60cafecd38346048d97b2","tid":2357914,"uid":200189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"晨早訂定 唔好比機會兩老幫襯藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://holaholi.com/5660/%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95%E9%BB%9E%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%962020-%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%98%BF%E8%94%94%E7%B3%95-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95-%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E7%B3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholaholi.com%2F5660%2F%25E8%25B3%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B3%2595%25E9%25BB%259E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%25962020-%25E8%25B3%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%2598%25BF%25E8%2594%2594%25E7%25B3%2595-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B3%2595-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B9%2584%25E7%25B3%2595%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=58878b2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://holaholi.com/5660/%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95%E9%BB%9E%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%962020-%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%98%BF%E8%94%94%E7%B3%95-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95-%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E7%B3%95/</a>"},{"pid":"314984ae7bc9cf350fb09fd5cf6bb1792de113d0","tid":2357914,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071748ab78eb81c7b3968787568f0ace2e3ad704","tid":2357914,"uid":200189,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:48:08.000Z","msg":"1. 富東閣海鮮酒家<br />\n富東閣賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/38QiLPK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38QiLPK&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=93211396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38QiLPK</a><br />\n地址：沙田瀝源街6號瀝源廣場1樓5號舖<br />\n電話：26998333<br />\n營業時間：星期一至日 07:00 &ndash; 23:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nView Map<br />\n2. Agape Garden 膳心小館<br />\n膳心小館賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3b64l0E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3b64l0E&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=6f01c44b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3b64l0E</a><br />\n自上年6月爆出「員工代通知金爆羅生門」事件後，膳心將產品主線移到網上平台、石硤尾店，以及聯乘其他同路人良心店。今年膳心小館推出6-8款賀年糕點，相信必定包括經典款－蘿蔔糕及芋頭糕，所以小編特意翻查去年的款式，睇下當中有無令你很期待的口味呢？小編會繼續更新有關消息！<br />\n地址：石硤尾白田街13號石硤尾邨美葵樓地下G06號舖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 不鳴 Gifvens<br />\n不鳴Gifvens是一間香港本地食物製造及網上零售商推出港產食物和禮品，一直堅守嚴選高品質食材，今年預告推出原味年糕、黑糖年糕、蘿蔔糕、紅豆年糕、紅棗杞子年糕、黃金馬蹄糕，更有靚靚禮盒包裝，真是令人非常期待！<br />\nFB：不鳴 Gifvens<br />\n不鳴 Gifvens之傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LiKWia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LiKWia&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=999c20b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LiKWia</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 團結<br />\n團結賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"http://instagram.com/p/CJfjmCcgB9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FCJfjmCcgB9C%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=acf8b363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FCJfjmCcgB9C%2F&h=8e49e30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/p/CJfjmCcgB9C/</a><br />\n<br />\n團結由多間香港小店組成，希望將經濟圈力量發揮到最大，透過資源共享，希望有更多人認識到不同嘅小店。糕點100%香港工場製造，係屬於香港人嘅無添加味道。今次聯合多間小店包括良糧 （＠excellentastehk）、到家元朗@joyhomecook 等合作單位推出瑤柱蘿蔔糕、五香芋頭糕、椰汁紅年糕及甜菊糖馬蹄糕，加上 初見（@first.sight_hk）包辦的靚靚包裝，送禮自用都好適合！<br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/p/CJfjmCcgB9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FCJfjmCcgB9C%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=acf8b363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FCJfjmCcgB9C%2F&h=8e49e30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/p/CJfjmCcgB9C/</a><br />\n<br />\n▸▸▸售賣平台：<br />\n1.良糧 （＠excellentastehk ）<br />\n▸<a href=\"http://etaste.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fetaste.com.hk&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=d0e90b10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">etaste.com.hk</a><br />\n2.正經嘢食 （＠jing_king_ye_sik）<br />\n▸<a href=\"http://jingkingfood.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjingkingfood.com&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=fb393be5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">jingkingfood.com</a><br />\n3.初見 First Sight_HK（@first.sight_hk）<br />\n4.到家元朗（＠joyhomecook）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 留家廚房 Kin&rsquo;s Kitchen<br />\n留家廚房賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3585alT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3585alT&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=59e53627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3585alT</a><br />\n<br />\n留家廚房被選為米芝蓮香港澳門2011一星食肆，質素有一定的保證！今年推出的賀年糕點包括「八鄉蘿蔔糕」丶「棕櫚糖年糕」丶「桂花馬蹄糕」和「紅棗椰汁糕」，所有糕點不含味精丶色素和防腐劑打造美味又健康的賀年糕點。<br />\n留家廚房<br />\n<br />\n地址：灣仔軒尼詩道314-324號 W Square 5樓<br />\n營業時間：12:00 &ndash; 15:00、18:00 &ndash; 23:00"},{"pid":"ec712bef9bf9b0f1585b05686e447f0ac53f6e35","tid":2357914,"uid":74383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df1f65051ea486ac83d60cafecd38346048d97b2","tid":2357914,"uid":200189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"晨早訂定 唔好比機會兩老幫襯藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://holaholi.com/5660/%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95%E9%BB%9E%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%962020-%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%98%BF%E8%94%94%E7%B3%95-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95-%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E7%B3%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholaholi.com%2F5660%2F%25E8%25B3%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B3%2595%25E9%25BB%259E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%25962020-%25E8%25B3%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%2598%25BF%25E8%2594%2594%25E7%25B3%2595-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B3%2595-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B9%2584%25E7%25B3%2595%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=58878b2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://holaholi.com/5660/%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95%E9%BB%9E%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%962020-%E8%B3%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%98%BF%E8%94%94%E7%B3%95-%E5%B9%B4%E7%B3%95-%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E7%B3%95/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"140aee8e2591b257205b40a4f1d272c56f37b13a","tid":2357914,"uid":200189,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:53:30.000Z","msg":"6. Thesteamhut 蒸廬<br />\n蒸廬 賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2X4ei6O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2X4ei6O&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=e422a5e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2X4ei6O</a><br />\n<br />\n蒸廬是高質點心黃店，於石門、黃埔各有分店，點心標榜即叫即做，用心烹調，籠仔荷葉蒸飯尤其出色。當然不少得賀年糕點，瑤柱臘味蘿蔔糕、奶黃年糕、蔗糖馬蹄糕3個選擇，一樣令人期待。<br />\n<br />\n地址：沙田石門安群街3號京瑞廣場一期2樓225號舖<br />\n電話：34603411<br />\n營業時間：星期一至五 11:30 &ndash; 21:00；星期六至日 08:30 &ndash; 21:00<br />\n<br />\n7/走肉朋友/蔬菜研究所<br />\n走肉朋友/蔬菜研究所 賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3odueQ7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3odueQ7&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=25f93614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3odueQ7</a><br />\n<br />\n在市面上要找到素食的蘿蔔糕年糕，可以講是難過登天！走肉朋友/蔬菜研究所推出一站式素黃賀年食品，除了賀年糕點，更有黃金油器及新年糖果！賀年糕點就有6個素食選擇，店家特別推介人氣黑糖年糕、夠薑年糕、香甜馬蹄糕 8及杞子棗皇糕，當然都有走肉版的家鄉芋頭糕及蘿蔔糕，素食猶不容錯過！<br />\n<br />\n地址：大角咀博文街28-30號地舖<br />\n電話：23886280<br />\n營業時間<br />\n星期一至五：11:30 &ndash; 15:00; 18:00 &ndash; 21:30 / 星期六至日 11:30 &ndash; 16:00;18:00 &ndash; 21:30<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8.徐記廚房點心<br />\n徐記廚房點心 賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2X7cGJp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2X7cGJp&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=512dbe7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2X7cGJp</a><br />\n<br />\n徐記廚房點心由徐媽媽主理，除了點心好食之外，每年重頭戲賀年糕點亦是精心預備，糕點全人手製作，不加防腐劑及色素，開放預訂的款式有臘味蘿蔔糕、五香芋頭糕、清甜鹿蹄糕（佢真係咁寫）、古法紅年糕、養顏紅棗糕！<br />\n<br />\n地址 ：太子花園街239號地下A號舖<br />\n電話：57210328／35639702<br />\n<br />\n9.叁拾士多<br />\n<br />\n叁拾士多是真正屬於香港人的士多，團隊一直為顧客搜羅優質食材及各類特色美食, 滿足香港人需要。而今年賀年系列糕點再度歸來，包裝盒設計延續去年青色麒麟作設計籃本，寓意趕走瘟神，而三款選擇包括蘿蔔糕，芋頭糕及伯爵茶年糕，絕對係百分百香港製造。<br />\n<br />\n叁拾士多<br />\n叁拾士多 賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3hHr704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3hHr704&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=7b26c9e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3hHr704</a><br />\n網店：<a href=\"https://30store.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F30store.hk%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=06af7655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://30store.hk/</a><br />\n叁拾士多：九龍觀塘成業街成業工業大廈3樓22室<br />\n叁拾士多Round 2：九龍荔枝角長沙灣道億利工業中心1樓10A室<br />\n叁拾士多 W：香港西環堅尼地城吉席街46至60A號吉豐大廈K號地舖<br />\n叁拾士多 F：新界大埔廣福道146號地下<br />\n<br />\n10.納雜<br />\n納雜 賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/38VSz6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38VSz6s&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=77121f73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/38VSz6s</a><br />\n<br />\n以大埔作基地大本營，專屬香港人嘅網上雜貨舖，支持本地蔬果及香港品牌。今年準備咗三款糕：分別係臘味蘿蔔糕、爽甜馬蹄糕同臘味芋頭糕，值得支持！<br />\n<br />\n網上購物平台：<a href=\"http://www.naapzaap.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.naapzaap.com&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=60900413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.naapzaap.com</a><br />\n<br />\n11.輕鬆煮 Cook Like Me<br />\n輕鬆煮 賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3rTTsFd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3rTTsFd&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=4ed68c94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3rTTsFd</a><br />\n<br />\n輕鬆煮 Cook Like Me營運三年，慢慢開始上軌道的時候，一直為顧客帶來全球易煮又好味的食物，今年開始制作自家賀年糕點，共有四款選擇：蘿蔔糕、芋頭糕、馬碲糕、椰汁年糕<br />\n<br />\n網上購物平台：<a href=\"http://cooklikemehongkong.boutir.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcooklikemehongkong.boutir.com&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=945d4d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cooklikemehongkong.boutir.com</a><br />\n<br />\n12.王孖記果子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/w.boysfruitstore/posts/4066690620010960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fw.boysfruitstore%2Fposts%2F4066690620010960&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=dc66efd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/w.boysfruitstore/posts/4066690620010960</a><br />\n<br />\n王孖記果子主打各種口味芒果糯米糍、特色健康果汁，其食品都是全人手新鮮製作！今年推出經典4款口味糕點 ：櫻花蝦黑松露蠔豉蘿蔔糕、椰汁斑蘭糕、黃金奶黃糕及蜜柑蘋果柚子蒟蒻凍糕，口味較市面上清新。<br />\n<br />\n地址：荔枝角青山道475A號地下A舖<br />\n營業時間：08:30 &ndash; 20:00<br />\n<br />\nView Details<br />\n13.延記<br />\n延記賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MvVFXn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MvVFXn&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=ca7311b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MvVFXn</a><br />\n<br />\n90後創業延記，以「香港人的最愛」港式點心延續下去，將充滿香港情懷點心傳揚，成立網店令香港人抗疫在家都可以飲個茶食個包，而今年第1年推出賀年糕點，主打足料瑤柱臘味蘿蔔糕及桂花金黃馬蹄糕。其它選擇包括：椰汁黃金糕、椰香紅棗糕及黑糖薑汁糕<br />\n<br />\nWtsapp: +852 6926 7005 (香港客服）<br />\n網上平台：<a href=\"http://www.theyinhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theyinhk.com&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=2363d45a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.theyinhk.com</a><br />\n<br />\n14.港優糧新春糕點<br />\n港優糧 賀年糕點之傳送門：<a href=\"https://urbanlicious.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Furbanlicious.hk%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=a63ea11e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://urbanlicious.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n港優糧新春糕點 透過有機耕種 、良食生產，將天然、健康和美味的食物帶到香港人的餐桌上，共享「香港原味道」。今次港優糧新春糕點 有農夫家臘味蘿蔔糕、甘香臘味芋頭糕、爽甜馬蹄糕3個選擇，而賀年禮品系更以蘿蔔糕+自家手工XO醬套裝。<br />\n<br />\n轉自 Holaholi 好想放假"},{"pid":"574ffb6c85e2f906750788