msI%3D&h=bb9f2672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=85260413518</a><br />\nHSBC：<br />\n741-383822-838<br />\n石牆花有限公司/Wall fare Group Limited<br />\n<br />\n*為保障公司戶口被質疑涉及洗黑錢活動，敬請以銀行戶口轉帳，避免以現金入數，多謝合作和體諒*<br />\n<br />\n訂購link👇👇截單為17/1/2021  7pm<br />\n訂購表格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeeGofk_-2YkhgSOwNrh3wol3hYexfhYXOIgY6atuwAioTv-Q/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeeGofk_-2YkhgSOwNrh3wol3hYexfhYXOIgY6atuwAioTv-Q%2Fviewform&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=0b9b6fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeeGofk_-2YkhgSOwNrh3wol3hYexfhYXOIgY6atuwAioTv-Q/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pUgqSPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUgqSPg.jpg&h=324d5ed4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf219437e4ad5093e1bdfcdf73ead3cceb4edad6","tid":2357914,"uid":2860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"574ffb6c85e2f906750788639413106b2fc36e5b","tid":2357914,"uid":218209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:55:00.000Z","msg":"逸東軒 糕點同禮盒<br />\n做緊8折promotion到1月17號<br />\nPush<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:48:10.000Z","msg":"有啲想訂佢哋嘅蘿蔔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bc1de9d06c6839ba061862d369aa5e3297fab5","tid":2357914,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買嘢一律買林泳淘洗頭水 同埋 鄧麗欣沐浴露<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2358931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2358931</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"490d339ce3d606c50ad739bd4173a247107daf92","tid":2357914,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T1